fields.name: Past, present, and future stats
fields.value:
- Yearly Stats - view your own or another player's yearly rotational stats.
- 2026 Stats - predict your own or another player's stats for the year 2026.
- 60 Day Historical Lookback - view historical rotational stats with a 60 day limit.
- Up to 3 Active Sessions - activate up to 3 sessions at one time.

fields.name: Customizability, ease of access, misc
fields.value:
- Unlock All Themes - get instant access to all voter themes without voting.
- No Command Cooldowns - remove cooldowns on commands ran.
- Username Autocomplete - be added to the username autocomplete options.
